        "title": "BLOS2 negatively regulates Notch signaling during neural and hematopoietic stem and progenitor cell development", 
        "published": "2016-10-10T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2016-10-10T00:00:00Z", 
        "volume": 5, 
